006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.schemagen;
007
008import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
009
010public class SchemaGenerationException
011    extends IllegalStateException {
012
013  /**
014   * the serial version UID.
015   */
016  private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;
017
018  public SchemaGenerationException() {
019    // use defaults
020  }
021
022  public SchemaGenerationException(String message, @NonNull Throwable cause) {
023    super(message, cause);
024  }
025
026  public SchemaGenerationException(String message) {
027    super(message);
028  }
029
030  public SchemaGenerationException(@NonNull Throwable cause) {
031    super(cause);
032  }
033
034}
